@startuml gabrielfarah_OpenHub

[GitHub API] as GitHub
[RabbitMQ] as RabbitMQ
[MongoDB] as MongoDB

package "Crawler" {
  [Crawler Script]
  [GitHub Client]
}

package "Worker Process" {
  [Worker Manager]
  
  package "Analysis Modules" {
    [Security Analysis]
    [Testability Analysis]
    [Reusability Analysis]
    [Usability Analysis]
  }
}

package "Configuration" {
  [Config Files]
}

Crawler --> GitHub : Fetches repository data
Crawler --> RabbitMQ : Publishes analysis tasks
Crawler --> MongoDB : Stores initial metadata

RabbitMQ --> "Worker Process" : Consumes analysis tasks

"Worker Process" --> GitHub : Downloads repository code
"Worker Process" --> MongoDB : Updates analysis results

"Worker Process" --> "Analysis Modules" : Uses

Crawler ..> "Configuration" : Reads
"Worker Process" ..> "Configuration" : Reads

@enduml